{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, you know, I could never understand how-- I mean how many, so many people-- because I knew there was about between 15,000 to 19,000 people, that there was that many-- where they were housed, you know?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, I remember that there was, on the hill, you know, from the men's barrack, you know, and there was, like, wires, you know, like a gated area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was women and children still in that particular camp at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you know, us they fed, you know, just soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave us some bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I mean, bread was-- you know, at that particular time, I wasn't a big eater.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some other people, you know, probably elderly people-- you know, I remember I ate very, very little, you know, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, sort of no appetite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't a big eater anyway at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But so actually, as far as food is concerned, you know, the starvation business didn't start till later on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not enough, but I mean, in Plaszow, you know-- like for instance, later on, I-- you know, the cooks, you know, would sometimes give you coffee.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially if they gave you some coffee with sugar in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I was able to, to take some and sell it, you know, and make a few zlotys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there was-- they used to bring in bread and salami and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't an everyday occurrence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once in a while, you know, we bought a little extra.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So me and my brother would share it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, you know, I remember I-- we went to work on a detail.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
